description: All parish events and Jersey's Liberation Square ceremony are amongst the cancellations.
title: Coronavirus: Liberation 75 events cancelled in Jersey and Guernsey
title_page: Coronavirus: Liberation 75 events cancelled in Jersey and Guernsey - BBC News
maintext: The Bailiff of Guernsey Sir Richard Collas said: "The community can rest assured that we remain committed to marking Liberation Day with due regard to the significance of the occasion and to the recognition our war-time generation are rightly due."
